# Patterns

- Prefer Form Request classes or explicit `$request->validate()` for input validation.
- Use Eloquent relationships and eager loading to avoid N+1 queries in Inertia props.
- Authorization: policies/gates; never rely on hidden form fields or client-side checks alone for sensitive actions.

# Inertia responses

- Return `Inertia::render('Page/Name', [...])` with only data the page needs; avoid dumping large unrelated models.

# Migrations

- Keep migrations reversible when possible; call out destructive changes (column drops, data backfills).

